title: Zuern Emerges Victorious on Opening Day of Saint Francis Health System ITA All-American Championships
text: won his first match in Pre-Qualifying Singles at the Saint Francis Health System ITA All-American Championships on Saturday at the Case Tennis Center at the University of Tulsa. Zuern cruised past Charlotte's Vikram Hundal 6-2, 6-1 on Saturday morning. He now advances to the Round of 128 agianst Buffalo's Amar Hromic at 9 a.m., EST/8 a.m., CST on Sunday. Winner of that match advances the Round of 64 that is also on Sunday against the winner of the match between Western Michigan's Ruben Greiner and MTSU's Gian Issa.
